Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能安排一位姓德溫特的先生坐她旁邊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}if a Mr. de Winter could sit with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-邁克西姆·德溫特先生嗎  -是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Monsieur Maxim de Winter? - Oui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特先生想坐在哪里  得看他自己的意思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It is the choice of Mr. de Winter where he wishes to be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  當然了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  是不夠嗎  我這里還有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So sorry. Is that not enough? Um, here. I've got more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  真抱歉  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}God, I'm so sorry, monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:03:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那么做  我聽說他是個非常粗魯無禮的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't do it. I've heard he's a terrible bore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -那個姓德溫特的家伙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Excuse me? - This de Winter chap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特先生  這邊請\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Monsieur de Winter, please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一打牡蠣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Des huîtres, une douzaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一打牡蠣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Des huîtres, une douzaine."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克西姆·德溫特\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maxim de Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是出人意料  我都不知道你在蒙特卡洛啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, I never. I had no idea you were in Monte.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你務必跟我們同桌用餐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You must join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊迪·范·霍珀  你應該記得我外甥比爾吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Edie Van Hopper. I think you remember my nephew. Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去年秋天在布倫海姆見過他  全名是比爾·惠特尼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You met him at Blenheim last fall. Billy Whitney. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他大概跟我差不多高\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's about my height.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的頭發是黃色的  眼睛有點弱視\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's got sandy hair and he's got a bit of a lazy eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的人我怎么可能忘記呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can't imagine how I could've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請代我向比爾問好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do give my regards to Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他結婚了  對方是一個非常迷人的姑娘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's married, and to the most enchanting girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是嗎  真好  -他寄來照片了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Is he? Good. - He sent photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以拿給你看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm going to show them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-過來  婚禮真的非常盛大  -我信你說的  \N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Come here. The wedding was divine. - I believe you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是希望獨自享用午餐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but I prefer to lunch alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日安  范·霍珀小姐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good day, Miss Van Hopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不是的  -什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Oh, no. - What? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有親緣關系  她就是個員工\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We're not related. She's staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許可以稱她為我的看護\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, I mean, I guess you could call her my ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  明白  失陪了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I see. Now, if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的  不如你去把照片拿過來吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Darling, why don't fetch those photographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我相信德溫特先生一定很想看看  -好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- I'm sure Mr. de Winter would love to see them. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  真的  拜托  別麻煩了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, please, please, please. Don't trouble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒必要拿  -親愛的  一點都不麻煩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- It's unnecessary. - Oh, my precious, it's no trouble at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不麻煩  去吧  快\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not at all. Go along. Quickly. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  她很快就會下來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, no. She'll be down in a jiffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是我最喜歡的部分\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, this is my favorite part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫她去把照片取下來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I asked her to go and get the photographs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從桌子邊飛快地沖出去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and she darts from the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她就走了  半天沒回來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and then she's gone. Doesn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想著  "天吶  別告訴我她開始畫畫了"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I thought, "Oh, God, don't tell me she started sketching."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  她真的是個小畫家  -天吶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Oh, no, no, she's an artist. - Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  她后來又跑下來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Anyway, she comes running back down,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渾身散發著濃濃的廉價玫瑰水味\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}reeking of cheap rose water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那氣味可真是熏死人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I mean, the smell of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一個黃金單身漢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Show me an eligible bachelor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會涌現一屋子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I will show you a room 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失心瘋一般的女人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}full of women acting like they've lost their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉  -沒事  坐下吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Sorry. - Never mind, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟說我們有親緣關系  想想看多離譜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Related. I mean, imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前很愛曼陀麗莊園的舞會  非常奢華迷人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I loved the Manderley ball. It was just so glamorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自從悲劇發生后  就再也沒舉辦過了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I suppose that's all stopped since the tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然發生了那種事  真叫人震驚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Such a shocking thing that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-要如何解釋啊  -太可怕了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- How do you explain it? - Awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那時深愛著她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He adored her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的呂蓓卡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}His Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  范·霍珀夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Morning, Mrs. Van Hopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,范·霍珀夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Van Hopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吐  我想吐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sick. I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我吐了一晚上了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm... I was sick all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快  快叫醫生來  -好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Call the... call the medecin. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-立刻叫醫生過來  -好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Call them right now. The doctor. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶在哪兒  桶在哪兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where is the bucket? Where's the bucket?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿桶  來  我拿著呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll get the bucket! Here, I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在等夫人嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You are waiting for madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  她病了  醫生叫她好好休息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, no. She's unwell. The doctor told her to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天只有我一個人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So, it's just me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不行的  露臺只允許貴客享用\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It is not possible. The terrace is for guests only.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是夫人的同伴\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But I'm a lady's companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  員工是不能使用的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, it is not for staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生  這位年輕小姐可以和我坐在一起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Monsieur? The young lady will be joining me. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再安排個座位吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Set another place, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題  德溫特先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Bien sûr, Monsieur de Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我無法承認這般盛情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, please. I couldn't possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's absolutely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且如果我們不想聊天  也可以不說話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And we needn't talk unless we feel like it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你不必為我這樣的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You... you didn't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的動機其實很自私\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}My motives were entirely selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是昨天的報紙  我都已經看過了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is yesterday's paper. I've already read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您的好意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you. It's very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這工作都做些什么  \N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So, what is it you do for...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是"貴婦伴侶"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm what's called "a lady's companion."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果貴婦需要出錢才能有伴\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If a lady has to pay for company,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那說明這位貴婦挺差勁的  不是嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that says something about the lady, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以點餐了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}May I take your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一打牡蠣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Des huîtres, une douzaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐吃這個嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你聽到的上  再續點咖啡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You heard her. Et encore du café.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  德溫特先生  小姐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Bien, Monsieur de Winter. Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請恕我冒昧  為何非得選擇她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If it's not rude, why her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你似乎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Seems like you would 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給很多人當伴侶都會非常出色\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}make an excellent companion for any number of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一直很喜歡到處旅行  \N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But I've always wanted to travel, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外  每年還有90鎊的薪水\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}so there's that, and £90 a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這些錢對你來說不算什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know that doesn't seem very much to you, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對我來說已經很多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but it's a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看的話  孤獨大概的確是有價格的吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I suppose you can set a price on loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪  不是嗎  有些人獨自一人似乎也過得很好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's odd, isn't it? Some people seem perfectly happy alone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有些人卻需要別人陪著一起度過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}while others just need someone to pass the time with. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是誰都沒關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Doesn't matter who.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪種\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Which are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母都已經去世了  所以...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, my parents are dead, so... 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我習慣了獨自一人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm used to being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的早餐來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Here comes your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用  一打牡蠣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Et voilà. Une douzaine d'huîtres.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都想嘗嘗  所以...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've always wanted to try them, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著還新鮮  快嘗嘗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Try them before they get warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太謝謝你了  感覺我從沒說過這么多話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you so much. I don't think I've ever spoken so much in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得很精彩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉我還點了牡蠣...  -不  沒事的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- And I'm sorry about the oysters, too. I... - No, that was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝你  我...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you very much. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久都沒那么開心過了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I haven't enjoyed myself like that for quite a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}À bientôt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-前臺有張字條給您  -謝謝  夫人身體不適\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- A note from the front desk. - Merci. Madame's indisposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我會轉交給她的  -是給您的  小姐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- I'll take it to her. - It's for you, mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What do they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(180,138)\frz25\fs12\bord0\shad0\c&H3b5c7a&}邁克西姆·德溫特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(210,208)\frz25\fs18\bord0\shad0\c&H000000&\fn手书体\b1}一起去兜風
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前臺  他們...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was just the front desk, they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道您怎么樣了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}wondering how you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么脫身的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So how did you escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我要上網球課\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I said I had a tennis lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直念叨我該增進球技\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She's been on at me to improve my game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Sneaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你想去哪里  -哪里都可以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- So where do you want to go? - Anywhere is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定有想看看的地方吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There must be somewhere you want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有點遠\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, it's quite far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯  正好呼吸新鮮空氣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good. I could use the fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是輛3.5升賓利嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is this a 3.5-liter Bentley?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  你怎么會這么了解車\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It is. How do you know so much about cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我父親  他生前很喜歡車\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, my father, he loved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否問一下  你的雙親是什么時候去世的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If I may ask, when did your parents pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前  死于流感\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Two winters ago. Influenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母親死于流感  我父親...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, my mother died of influenza, and my...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天后也去了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}father died just four days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得會有人死于心碎嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you think a person could die of a broken heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我說話欠考慮了  對不起  -沒事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- That was thoughtless of me. I'm sorry. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才叫兜風\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(340,40)}異國植物園
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實有棵仙人掌  原長于墨西哥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There's actually a cactus, it's native to Mexico,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能長到65英尺高\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and it grows to 65 feet tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以活200年  但從第70年起才能開花\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It lives for 200 years, but it doesn't flower until it's 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都是從哪里學到這些的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where do you learn this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從某處讀來的  我知道的一切都來自書本\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I read about it somewhere. Everything I know is from books.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒見過什么大世面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I haven't really experienced anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我打算趁年輕好好經歷一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I plan to before I'm old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來過這里嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Have you been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多年前  度蜜月時來過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Years ago. On my honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你夫人是怎么  -拜托  別說這個了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- How did your wife... - Please... let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mr. de Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-去開吧  -不行  我不能開\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Go on. - Oh, no. I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以的  你會開不是嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes. Yes, you can. You know how, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是會  可我...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, yes, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  只要不是從書上學的就好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, good. As long as you didn't learn from a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和我說說曼陀麗莊園嗎  聽說那里很美\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Will you tell me about Manderley? I hear it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確很美\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It is. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼陀麗不只是座宅邸  它是我生活的全部\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Manderley, it's more than a house. It's my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾個世紀來都是由父輩把它傳給子輩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's been passed from father to son and father to son for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少延續至今\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Until now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我無后而終  就要交由我姐姐繼承\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You see, if I die without an heir, it goes to my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的兒子們都是好孩子  只不過不姓德溫特\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And her sons are nice boys, but they're just not de Winters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你讓我們安全到達了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, thank you for getting us home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了拿好你的東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't forget your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生  能請你幫個忙嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Sir, would you give us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}異國植物園
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}《愛情詩選集》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你幫我做這個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is what I need from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你抓著棚蓋  和我同時抬起來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Would you grab that bag and just lift at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呂蓓卡贈邁克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你放回去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Put that back, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  對不起...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, of course. I'm sorry. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙留給停車員就好  晚安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Leave the keys with the valet. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護士一小時前就走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The nurse left an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網球教練只剩晚上有免費課\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The tennis coach only had a late session free...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那練習發球\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I was practicing my serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸黑上網球課嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A tennis lesson in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克斯贈呂蓓卡  呂蓓卡贈邁克斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Rebecca from Max. Max from Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傻丫頭  為什么要看他的私人書本\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You stupid girl. Why would I look at his personal book?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您的  是德溫特先生留的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For you. From Monsieur de Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}邁克西姆·德溫特\N去卡普代享用午餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我的嗎  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pour moi? Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我要走了  -你穿的什么衣服\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- I'm off. - What have you got on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都能看見里面了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can see right through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你穿內衣了吧  -當然\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- You wearing any undergarments? - Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(200,112)\frz-22\fs12\bord0\shad0\c&H2b497a&}邁克西姆·德溫特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(180,178)\frz-22\fs18\bord0\shad0\c&H303040&\fn手书体\b1}去摩納哥城散步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想畫那些漂亮的房子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm trying to paint those beautiful houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不著網球拍  好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Actually, you don't need your tennis racket. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在做什么  -你馬上就知道了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- What are you doing? - Oh, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下  如果能把回憶像香水一樣裝進瓶子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Imagine if you could bottle a memory like scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想開啟它  就能隨時開啟它\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then, whenever you wanted, you could open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像把那一瞬重新度過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It'd be like living the moment all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你如此年輕的生命里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And what particular moments
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把哪些瞬間裝進瓶子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}in your young life would you bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星期  此時此刻  每一分鐘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This week. Now. Every minute of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會忘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有不想要的回憶  就可以干脆丟掉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And any memories you didn't want, you could simply throw away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"一起去兜風"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Come for a drive."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"去卡普代享用午餐"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Lunch at the Cap."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海灘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我喜歡這里的海岸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But I love the coast down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好美\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, there we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那個是...  -讓我看看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Um, well, it's... - Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是你  我不會看的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, I wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  幸好你并不是我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No... Well, it's just as well you're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-對不起  -沒關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Sorry. - That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  我們去游泳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on. Let's go for a swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  走吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快下來  -不了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Come in! - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-為什么不  -我不想下來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Why not? - I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在怕什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水太冷  要凍壞了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's too cold. No, it's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷  很舒服\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, it's not. It's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺得到  太冰了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can feel it. It's freezing cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你快過來  -不  我要去把香檳喝光\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- You come here! - No. I'm gonna drink all the champagne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無所謂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  瞧瞧你逼我做了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}God! Look at what you're making me do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你起來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:20:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好轉了真是太好了  護士呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm so glad you're feeling better. Where's the nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打發走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你像是游過泳  打完網球后游的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Took a swim, I see. After tennis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  擦干頭發  快去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, go on. Dry your hair. Chop-chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要下去吃晚餐嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are we going down for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以安排前臺服務生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You can see the concierge about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我們訂明天的早班火車票了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}booking us on the early train tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李也可以開始打包了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And you can set about packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Um, tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比爾周六啟航去紐約\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Billy is sailing for New York on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以乘同一艘船\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We can catch the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在歐洲待得煩死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sick to death of Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這么失魂落魄地看著我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't look at me like a drowned rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就能習慣紐約的生活\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You'll get used to New York fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人多得是  到處都新鮮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Plenty of boys and excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且都和你門當戶對\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All in your own class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以為人們不會議論嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Did you really think people wouldn't talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷了是好事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, you're best out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都知道她去世后他差點瘋了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Everyone knows he nearly lost his mind after she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸來得太突然了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was all too sudden and tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會真以為他愛上你了吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you honestly think he is in love with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是拿你散散心  僅此而已\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was a distraction, dear. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要離開了  到紐約去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We'll go away. We'll go to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會找到你的出路的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You'll find your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會把這一切都忘掉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You'll forget all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  你會把這一切都忘掉的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Trust me, you will forget all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,范·霍珀夫人要走了  我也必須離開\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Van Hopper is leaving and I have to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在說什么  -真的  就現在  今天就走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- What are you talking about? -Yes. Now. Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想跟你道個別\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I just wanted to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:22:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么沒和我提過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why haven't you told me before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她昨晚才決定的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Because she only decided it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去巴黎  和她的外甥碰面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And we're going to Paris with... to meet her nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去瑟堡乘船去紐約\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then we go to Cherbourg to sail to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  你別哭\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All right. Listen, you mustn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一點時間想想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just give me a moment to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能久留  她讓我在樓下等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can't stay long. She's expecting me downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去曼陀麗莊園\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}To Manderley.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  當你的秘書嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What? As your secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我的妻子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}As my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在向你求婚  小傻瓜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm asking you to marry me, you little fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.07,0:23:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能去曼陀麗莊園\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can't come to Manderley.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當然可以  你說過你想看看這世界\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, you can. You said you wanted to see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼陀麗就是這世上最美好的地方\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Manderley is the best part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她當然在大廳  不然能去哪里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, of course she's down there. Where else is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我20分鐘后就要出發去趕火車了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, I've got to leave in 20 minutes to catch the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我去跟她說  -真的要去嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- I'll tell her. - Do we have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.03,0:24:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...當然要去了  其實我還挺想去會會她的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, in fact... Yes, we do. I'm actually looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.61,0:24:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等的就是這句話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's exactly what I'm waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Now, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.07,0:24:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是誰啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Who is this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我這輩子聽到過的最好的消息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is the most wonderful news I've ever heard in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想趕緊告訴我的朋友們  太不可思議了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wait till I tell my friends, I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算怎么安排婚事  拜托了  全都告訴我吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What are the plans? Please. I must know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.49,0:24:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經安排好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, the plans are settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.53,0:24:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就在這里結婚  在歐洲度蜜月\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We'll marry here, and honeymoon in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.45,0:24:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回家  回曼陀麗莊園\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And then home to Manderley.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.57,0:24:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.57,0:24:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這輩子還沒聽過這么浪漫的話吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Have you ever heard of anything more romantic in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"回曼陀麗莊園"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Home to Manderley."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.32,0:24:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  那可是童話故事里才有的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, my goodness. It's out of a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.78,0:24:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我先去打點一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All right. I'll go and make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.24,0:24:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你的行李就要上火車了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}your bags don't end up on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.70,0:24:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是要快點  -你沒事的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Do hurry. - You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.53,0:24:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧  我們有太多事情要聊了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, yes, go along. We have lots to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.82,0:24:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天吶  你動作還挺快啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, goodness gracious, don't you work quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.65,0:24:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有做一些你不該做的事嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Have you been doing things you shouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.61,0:25:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你在說什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.74,0:25:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過幸好你家人都不在了  不用向他們解釋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, you don't have a family, luckily, to explain it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.32,0:25:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事我就不管了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I wash my hands of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.36,0:25:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了曼陀麗莊園  肯定會安排個工作給你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Gonna have your work cut out for you at Manderley.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.82,0:25:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說  我覺得你不能勝任\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And, frankly, I don't think you're up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.32,0:25:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我可以學  -這么跟你說吧  親愛的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- I can learn. - Let me tell you something, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.15,0:25:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用性拴住男人很容易\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When you trap a man between your legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.65,0:25:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們不會留戀\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}they don't stick around for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.57,0:25:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  范·霍珀夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Goodbye, Mrs. Van Hopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.32,0:25:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他娶你單純是因為不想在那間老舊的大宅子里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's only marrying you because he doesn't want to go on living
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.32,0:25:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她的鬼魂度過余生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}in that big old house with her ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.40,0:25:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信有鬼魂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't believe in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.99,0:26:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  我最討厭他們這一套了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, God. I hate it when they do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.74,0:26:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能低調一點嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So much for keeping things quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.28,0:26:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道她的  老爺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know how she is, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.61,0:26:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在曼陀麗有曼陀麗的規矩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There's a way things are done at Manderley.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.45,0:27:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的  這是弗里思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Darling, this is Frith.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.15,0:27:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.45,0:27:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是正式一點吧  來  起來咯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let's do things properly, shall we? There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.86,0:27:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你干什么呢  -怎么  你不喜歡啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- What are you doing? - What? You don't like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.03,0:27:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上肩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Up you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.20,0:27:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣了  邁克斯  放我下來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't, Max, put me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.65,0:27:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯太太\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Danvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.82,0:27:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到曼陀麗莊園\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Welcome to Manderley.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.53,0:27:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  見到你很高興\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hello. It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.99,0:28:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝  -茶泡好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Thank you. Thank you. - Tea is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.32,0:28:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯是這兒的管家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Danvers runs the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.15,0:28:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怕  她沒看起來那么嚇人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't worry, she's not as scary as she seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.82,0:28:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克西姆  這里太棒了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, Maxim, it's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.15,0:28:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吠了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.20,0:28:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游子可算回來了  見到你很高興  邁克斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There he is. The wanderer returns. Good to see you, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.28,0:28:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我也是  弗蘭克  -旅途如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- And you, Frank. - How was the trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.32,0:28:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還挺豐富多彩的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Was rather eventful, as it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.95,0:28:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我是弗蘭克·克勞利  德溫特夫人  -幸會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Frank Crawley, Mrs. de Winter. - It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.57,0:28:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  你好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.86,0:28:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克是地產管理人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Frank's the estate manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.53,0:28:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里沒了他可就完蛋了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The place would fall apart without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.15,0:28:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他言過其實了  別聽他的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ah, no, no. He exaggerates. Ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.70,0:28:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想掃興  但我有幾份文件急需你簽名\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I, I hate to be a bore, but I urgently need a few signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.82,0:28:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證只借走他一下  馬上還給你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I promise I'll have him back to you in a jiffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.11,0:28:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們走吧  -好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Shall we? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.03,0:28:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯  帶德溫特夫人轉一圈  好嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Danvers, show Mrs. de Winter the house. Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.99,0:28:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  沒關系的  我等你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, no, that's all right. I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.45,0:29:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別犯傻了  去吧  我過會兒來找你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, don't be silly. Go on. I'll catch you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.74,0:29:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座莊園已經在這家族名下三百多年了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The estate has been in the family for over 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.03,0:29:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是亨利八世贈予的禮物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was originally a gift from Henry VIII.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.40,0:29:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太非凡了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.32,0:29:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有客人來了  您可以用客廳招待\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If there are guests, you may use the drawing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.28,0:29:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得告訴弗里思  讓他點燃爐火\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't forget to tell Frith to light the fires,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.53,0:29:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一般來說  老爺喜歡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but generally, Mr. de Winter prefers
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.78,0:29:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在書房這里喝咖啡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to take his coffee here in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.78,0:29:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好有你在  丹弗斯太太\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Glad you're here, Mrs. Danvers. I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.74,0:29:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我肯定記不住這一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll Never remember all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.74,0:29:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(50,40)\fs18\fn手书体\b1\bord0\shad0\fsp-2\frz5\c&H300000&}呂蓓卡·德溫特\N弗蘭克·克勞利先生\N曼陀麗莊園\N康沃爾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.90,0:29:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您擔心的是這個  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, I'm sure you won't disappoint him, madam,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.74,0:29:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一定不會讓他失望的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}if that's your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.65,0:29:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特家族可追溯到都鐸王朝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The de Winter family dates back to the Tudors.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.49,0:29:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And, um, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.07,0:30:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是卡羅琳·德溫特  老爺的姑婆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's Caroline de Winter. Mr. de Winter's great aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.15,0:30:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好嫵媚動人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She's very striking.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.53,0:30:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  她可是英國第一批\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, and one of the first women
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.61,0:30:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得醫生執照的女性之一\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to qualify as a doctor in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.20,0:30:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是其中一幅老爺最喜歡的畫作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's one of his favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.78,0:30:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都睡在哪兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where does everyone sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.20,0:30:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女仆睡閣樓  男仆睡地下室\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maids in the attic, men below stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.07,0:30:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該和你待過的地方一個規矩吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}just as in your other houses, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.95,0:30:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒見過這么壯觀的大宅\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Never even seen a house like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.40,0:30:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我以為你當過貼身女仆呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, I'm sorry. I thought you'd been a lady's maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.45,0:30:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主臥現在搬到東廂了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The master bedroom is now in the east wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.36,0:30:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這花紋真好看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What a... pretty pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.15,0:30:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是克拉麗斯  在您的女仆來之前負責服侍您\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is Clarice. She'll look after you until your maid gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.99,0:30:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有雇女仆  不過我自己能應付得過來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't have a maid, but I'm sure I'll manage without one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.61,0:31:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會需要一個的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, I think you'll find you need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.87,0:31:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓克拉麗斯來吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Perhaps Clarice could take the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.99,0:31:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里看不見大海\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You can't see the sea from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.82,0:31:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看不見\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.32,0:31:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老爺要他以前的衣櫥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Should Mr. de Winter ask for his old wardrobe,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.57,0:31:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕您得告訴他這里會放不下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm afraid you must tell him it wouldn't fit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.74,0:31:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住宅這一面的房間要小很多\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The rooms on this side of the house are much smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.86,0:31:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里以前不是他的臥室嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This wasn't his bedroom before?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.90,0:31:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  德溫特夫人的房間都在西廂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, no, no. No. Mrs. de Winter's rooms were in the west wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.24,0:31:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里多好啊  空著太可惜了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, it's a lovely room. Much too nice to stand empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.15,0:31:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客房都不會空閑太久的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The guest rooms are never empty for very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.45,0:31:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特夫人還在世時  我們辦過很多次宴會\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We did a lot of entertaining when the late Mrs. de Winter was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.61,0:31:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼陀麗舞會在當時可是件大事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The Manderley ball was quite an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.70,0:31:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓克拉麗斯陪您了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll leave you with Clarice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.99,0:31:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我個問題\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ask me a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.95,0:32:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么問題\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What sort of question?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.11,0:32:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.07,0:32:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你毫無保留\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I have no secrets from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.65,0:32:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我們結婚了  難道不應該坦誠相待嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't you think that's how it should be now that we're married?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.99,0:32:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的婚姻都隱藏著秘密\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All marriages have their secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.11,0:32:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意  可以和我說說她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You can talk to me about her... if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.03,0:32:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  親愛的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good night, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.87,0:33:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maxim?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.49,0:34:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.28,0:34:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫醒夢游的人很危險\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's dangerous to wake a sleepwalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.95,0:35:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  但馬廄需要翻修屋頂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And nothing to worry about, but the stables will need reroofing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.74,0:35:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為瓦片都腐爛了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}because the tiles are spoiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.15,0:35:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-早上好  親愛的  -早上好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Good morning, darling. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.07,0:36:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-睡得怎么樣  -挺好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Sleep well? - Yes, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.70,0:36:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.11,0:36:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-您適應得如何  -非常好  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- How are you settling in? - Very well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.78,0:36:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  那就好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.49,0:36:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去上面等您\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll... see you up there, shall I?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.86,0:36:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我馬上就來  -再見  德溫特夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Won't be a sec. - Mrs. de Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.95,0:36:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  克勞利先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mr. Crawley.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.20,0:36:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我弗蘭克就好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Frank. It's Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.53,0:36:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該早點起床的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I should have got up earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.78,0:36:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們就能共用早餐了  -沒關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- We could have had breakfast together. - Oh, that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.86,0:36:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你會夢游嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Did you know you sleepwalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.40,0:36:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享用早餐吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Enjoy your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.11,0:37:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰斯珀\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.36,0:37:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪兒  杰斯珀\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where are you going? Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.53,0:37:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰斯珀  你跑去哪了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Jasper, where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.30,0:37:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呂
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.15,0:37:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}曼陀麗莊園賓客名冊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.45,0:37:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}克羅斯比與福克斯內衣坊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.03,0:38:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}假面舞會
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.28,0:39:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打擾各位...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sorry to disturb you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.07,0:39:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉麗斯  你看見老爺了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Clarice, have you seen Mr. de Winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.99,0:39:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有藥膏嗎  我割傷手了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And do you have a plaster? I've cut my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.65,0:39:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.61,0:39:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒什么大礙  我沒事  -天吶  等一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Really, it's nothing. I'm fine. - Oh, my. One moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.95,0:39:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好你在  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Since you're here, madam,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.32,0:39:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問今天的菜單是不是合意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}may I have your approval for today's menus?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.36,0:39:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  非常合適  我完全滿意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes. Good. Very suitable. Very nice indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.11,0:39:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-烤小牛肉的醬汁呢  -那款看起來非常好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- And the sauce for the roast veal? - Yes, that looks excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.65,0:39:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我空著沒填\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, but I've left it blank, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.78,0:39:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特夫人非常講究醬汁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. de Winter was most particular about her sauces.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.15,0:39:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Right. Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.95,0:39:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按德溫特夫人的喜好來吧  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We'll have whatever Mrs. de Winter would have had. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.65,0:39:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Very well, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.40,0:39:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了  -非常感謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- There we go. - Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.86,0:40:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呂
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.86,0:40:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎  親愛的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is everything all right, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.74,0:40:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想從倫敦訂一些新內衣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was thinking of... ordering some new undergarments from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.99,0:40:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶蕾絲的內衣  還要一套睡衣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Something lacy and a nightgown.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.70,0:40:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么時候抱怨過你的穿著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When have I ever complained about what you wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.78,0:40:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真好  對吧  你我二人世界\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is nice, isn't it? Just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.40,0:40:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像回到了度蜜月的時候\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's almost like we're back on our honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.11,0:40:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好懷念啊  你呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, I miss it. Don't you?
