Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.28,0:47:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上車吧  奶奶  來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Listen, let's get in the car, Granny. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.07,0:47:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從花房拿的  希望可以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is from the flower room. I hope that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.20,0:47:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝  -對不起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Thank you. - Look, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.95,0:47:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記奶奶有多喜歡呂蓓卡了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'd forgotten how fond our grandmother was of Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.95,0:48:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.57,0:48:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是那么氣人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She was just one of those bloody annoying people.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.95,0:48:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都無法抗拒她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Irresistible to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.27,0:48:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是男人  女人  孩子  還是動物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The men, women, children, animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.86,0:48:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些凡人根本沒法比\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Us mere mortals couldn't hope to compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.78,0:48:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-老爺  -他哭什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Sir. - Why is he crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.61,0:48:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺  晨室里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Sir, one of the porcelain pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.61,0:48:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件瓷器不見了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}is missing from the morning room,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.82,0:48:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在丹弗斯太太要開除這個男孩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and now Danvers is calling for the boy's dismissal.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.07,0:48:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但不是...  -哪一件\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- But it wasn't... - Which piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.57,0:48:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不確定  老爺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We're not sure, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.45,0:48:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯太太\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Danvers!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.45,0:49:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒什么事吧  -沒事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Is everything all right? - Yes, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.36,0:49:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨室里有樣東西不見了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Something rather's just gone missing from the morning room.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.30,0:49:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.03,0:49:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-丹弗斯太太  -什么東西不見了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Danvers! - What is it? What's gone missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.61,0:49:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么覺得是羅伯特拿的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What on earth makes you think Robert took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.57,0:49:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德累斯頓瓷器非常值錢  老爺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The Dresden is extremely valuable, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.99,0:49:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不是我干的  -單那一件就價值一百多鎊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- But it wasn't me! - That piece alone is worth £100.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.15,0:49:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-老爺  不太可能是...  -那是誰干的  弗里思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Sir, I find it most unlikely... - Then who, Frith?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.99,0:49:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干雜活的女仆是不能進晨室的  我負責收拾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The between maid isn't allowed in the morning room. I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.82,0:49:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特夫人還在世的時候  我們一起收拾瓷器\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When Mrs. de Winter was alive, we did it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.99,0:49:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-弗里思只是說...  -是我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- All Frith is saying... - It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.20,0:49:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我打碎的  它碎了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I broke it. It broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.90,0:49:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心打碎的  它掉到地上了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was an accident. It fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.82,0:49:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  真相大白\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.65,0:49:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伯特  你沒事了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Robert, you're off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.57,0:49:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片在哪兒  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where are the pieces, madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.65,0:49:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在后面的書桌抽屜里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}In the bureau drawer at the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.86,0:50:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄到倫敦去  丹弗斯太太  看能不能修補\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Send them to London, Danvers. See if anything can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.15,0:50:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  老爺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Certainly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.45,0:50:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再發生這種事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And may I suggest, should anything like this happen again,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.78,0:50:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特夫人能不能直接告訴我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that Mrs. de Winter tell me herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.28,0:50:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒事了吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If we're all quite finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.58,0:50:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呂
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.49,0:52:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.45,0:52:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. de Winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.65,0:52:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你跟邁克斯去倫敦了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I thought you'd gone up to London with Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.40,0:52:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在倫敦嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's in London?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.99,0:52:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  去處理文件了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah. Taking care of some paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.24,0:52:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他讓我給這里加把鎖  我差點把你鎖在里面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He asked me to put a padlock on here. I nearly locked you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.32,0:52:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.11,0:52:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里要荒廢了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This place going to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.90,0:52:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒船了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well... no boat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.20,0:52:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克斯不喜歡駕船出海\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Max doesn't like to sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.15,0:52:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝恩說她是淹死的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ben said she drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.36,0:52:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我以為你知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sorry. I assumed you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.45,0:53:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不知道  -那天天氣很差\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- No. - Ah, it's... It was brutal weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.78,0:53:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便對她這個好駕船人來說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Even for her. She was an excellent sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.86,0:53:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船沉了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The boat went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.70,0:53:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒找到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They never recovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.32,0:53:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月后她被沖上了埃奇庫姆的岸邊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She washed up in Edgcumbe some... two months later.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.57,0:53:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月  天吶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Two months? My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.90,0:53:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Poor Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.82,0:53:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我載他去認了尸體\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Drove him down there myself to identify the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.24,0:53:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必為過去所擾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know, you really mustn't dwell on the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.53,0:53:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們很般配  他已經走出來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're so good for Max. He's a changed man.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.95,0:53:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她當時一定很害怕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She must have been so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.57,0:53:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在海上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Out there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.95,0:53:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她什么都不怕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She wasn't afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.40,0:53:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能問你點事嗎  弗蘭克  跟我說實話\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Can I ask you something, Frank? And promise to tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.36,0:54:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不公平  我還不知道你要問什么呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hardly fair, isn't it. Don't know what you're gonna ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.36,0:54:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蓓卡很美嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Was Rebecca very beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.49,0:54:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.65,0:54:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, I suppose she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.36,0:54:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這輩子見過的最美的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}the most beautiful creature I ever saw in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.99,0:55:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呂
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.99,0:55:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裙子的確很美  不是嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It is beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.11,0:55:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它照原樣放著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I keep it just the way it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.24,0:55:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像她只是出去一會兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's as if she'd just gone out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.78,0:55:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嚇了我一跳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.11,0:55:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件是她的最愛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This was her favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.49,0:55:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚我替她擺在床上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I laid it out for her that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.74,0:55:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  拿著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Go on, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.74,0:55:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.95,0:55:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不要貼身女仆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She wouldn't have a lady's maid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.70,0:55:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說  "丹尼  我除了你誰也不要"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"I don't want anyone but you, Danny."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.95,0:56:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到她有多高了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you see how tall she was?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.53,0:56:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以她的身材穿什么都很好看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hmm. She could wear anything with a figure like hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.11,0:56:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚我都會替她梳頭發\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'd brush her hair for her every evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.32,0:56:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會說  "快來  丹尼  幫我梳頭發"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Come on, Danny, hair drill." she'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.32,0:56:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會站在她身后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'd stand behind her
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.99,0:56:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次為她梳上20分鐘\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and brush away for 20 minutes at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.82,0:56:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有一頭濃密的深色秀發\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That great mass of dark hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.61,0:56:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會加入\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He joined in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.82,0:56:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很喜歡為她這樣做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He loved to do that for her.
