Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.05,1:04:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克·費弗爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Jack Favell.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.07,1:04:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你邀請他來喝茶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You asked him for tea,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.09,1:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知道老爺不準他來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}knowing full well Mr. de Winter has banned him from the property.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.35,1:04:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是弄錯了  夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There must be some mistake, madam.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.12,1:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有一年多沒見過費弗爾先生了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I haven't seen Mr. Favell for over a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.60,1:04:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  弗里思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hello, Frith.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.90,1:05:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  老爺  費弗爾先生不請自來過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hello, sir. Mr. Favell has made an unannounced visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.31,1:05:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管她對弗里思說了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't care what she told Frith!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.11,1:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費弗爾先生跟我說是她邀請他來這兒的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mr. Favell told me that she invited him here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.20,1:05:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是丹弗斯太太逼你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, Mrs. Danvers, I suppose she forced you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.41,1:05:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他一起騎馬的嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to go riding with him, did she?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.84,1:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我可以解釋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, I can explain!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.24,1:05:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-解釋什么  -我本來打算告訴你的  真的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Explain what? - I was going to tell you, I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.35,1:05:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想告訴我你是怎么把他拉到船庫里的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Want to tell me how you dragged him down to the boathouse?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.21,1:05:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么跟他展示你漂亮的新睡衣嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Parade your fancy new night clothes for him?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.44,1:05:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能這么想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How could you even think that?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.51,1:05:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我知道你會生氣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'd never have let him on the property
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.28,1:05:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會讓他進入莊園  邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}if I'd known it would upset you, Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.09,1:05:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  我愛你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.61,1:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.63,1:05:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丹弗斯太太邀請他過來的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Danvers invited him here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.32,1:05:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再聽到你說丹弗斯了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't wanna hear another word about Danvers!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.56,1:06:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.44,1:06:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯太太\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Danvers.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.49,1:06:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來辭退你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've come to give you your notice.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.73,1:06:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺同意了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Has Mr. de Winter agreed to this?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.88,1:06:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的決定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The decision is mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.66,1:06:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You see...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.58,1:06:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從呂蓓卡小時候就開始照顧她了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I looked after Rebecca when she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.54,1:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她結婚之后  我們一起來到了這里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We came here together when she was first married.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.53,1:06:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是她的朋友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was her friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.31,1:06:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以分享她秘密的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Someone to share her secrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.90,1:06:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種關系是無法打破的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Bond like that can't be broke.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.67,1:07:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法取代  我不該期望和您建立這種關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Can't be replaced. I was wrong to expect that from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.54,1:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會找到另一個莊園\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, you'll find another house.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.58,1:07:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.01,1:07:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們女人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We women,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.74,1:07:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么結婚  要么去當仆人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}we can either marry or go into service,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.90,1:07:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太老了  這兩種選擇都不合適\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I'm too old for either.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.78,1:07:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會確保你衣食無憂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, we'll make sure that you're provided for.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.16,1:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和錢無關  只是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, it's not about money. It's...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.35,1:07:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對我來說不是工作  呂蓓卡是我的人生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This wasn't a job for me. Rebecca was my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.59,1:07:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.10,1:07:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我讓您失望了  我很抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sorry if I failed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.21,1:07:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我的本意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I didn't mean to let you down.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.60,1:07:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是您看上去一心想要我行我素\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was just you seemed so set on doing things your own way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.11,1:07:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這一切對我來說都很陌生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No. This is all very new to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.80,1:07:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個莊園  還有傭人...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The house, the staff...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.53,1:07:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.10,1:07:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得德溫特先生也希望你能幫我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I think that Mr. de Winter hoped that you'd help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.48,1:08:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您并沒有向我尋求幫助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You didn't ask for my help.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.13,1:08:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.91,1:08:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我現在請求你的幫助呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}what if I asked for it now?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.66,1:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.64,1:08:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個蠢貨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.80,1:08:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的錯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.20,1:08:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道不是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.54,1:09:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.80,1:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}曼陀麗舞會
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.74,1:09:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}曼陀麗舞會
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.86,1:09:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.33,1:09:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}開胃菜  牡蠣
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.82,1:09:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  夫人  我馬上去印出來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Very good, madam. Perfect. I'll have them printed at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.81,1:09:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您希望倫敦的沃斯店定制您的服裝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, and we must let Voce in London know before Friday
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.42,1:09:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須在周五之前通知他們\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}if you wish them to make your costume.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.51,1:09:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  恐怕我還沒有做好決定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes. I'm afraid I'm drawing a bit of a blank there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.88,1:09:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是舞會上最重要的女士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, you'll be the most important lady at the ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.92,1:09:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-選擇服裝的時候請謹記這一點  -好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- So, choose something with that in mind. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.49,1:09:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信點\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, be confident.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.88,1:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們看看您的自然美\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let them see your natural beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.57,1:10:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Madam?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.67,1:10:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我這么說不會太冒昧的話...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If it's not too forward of me...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.96,1:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯太太說  您還沒有決定要穿什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Danvers said you'd not picked out what to wear yet, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.98,1:10:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道您想不想聽聽我的建議\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I wondered if you'd want an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.08,1:10:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  當然  什么建議都可以  坐吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, please, anything. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.56,1:10:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫廊里的那些舊畫作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just... the old paintings in the gallery.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.75,1:10:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直認為畫里的服裝會是最漂亮的舞會禮服\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I always thought they'd make the most beautiful costume.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.58,1:10:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是身穿紅裙的那位女士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Especially the lady in the red dress.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.14,1:10:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明智的選擇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Brilliant choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.43,1:10:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉麗斯和我說了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Clarice informed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.84,1:10:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請容許我說  這件裙子配得上莊園的女主人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And if I may say so, one worthy of the lady of this house.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.56,1:10:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I do apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.75,1:11:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}公爵和公爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.43,1:11:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}禮炮煙花
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.91,1:11:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  把這個拿給丹弗斯太太好嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Right. Will you take this down to Mrs. Danvers?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.37,1:11:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-確保她把一切準備妥當  -好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Make sure she has everything. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.96,1:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-多謝  -如果你們一直走到大宅...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Thank you very much. - And if you go through to the house...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.29,1:11:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抱歉  -我很抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Oh, sorry. - I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.27,1:11:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-歡迎  歡迎  -你還好嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Welcome. Welcome. - Are you quite all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.70,1:11:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是的  現在有點風  弗蘭克  -是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Yes. There's bit of a wind, Frank. - Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.57,1:11:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-希望不會下雨  -肯定不會的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Hope it doesn't rain. - It'll come to nothing, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.56,1:11:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.90,1:11:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}沃斯
