Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.04,1:12:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  你會毀了驚喜的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, no, no, no, no, you'll ruin the surprise.
