Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.79,1:21:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕不會愛你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He'll never love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.55,1:21:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什么要愛你呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And why should he?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.44,1:21:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他愛過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He did.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.34,1:21:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他無法愛上你  因為你不是她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, he can't love you because you're not her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.02,1:21:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真該見見她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You should've seen her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.34,1:21:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在16歲時  她騎著父親的馬  那馬野得很\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}At 16 years old, on her father's horse, a huge brute,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.67,1:21:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她馴服了它\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but she mastered him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.04,1:21:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她調教完馬后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}By the time she finished with him,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.23,1:21:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已經順服得像羊羔一般\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}he was nothing but froth and blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.78,1:21:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓她失望了  由得你在這里住了這么久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've let her down, allowing you here for so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.87,1:21:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她無法容忍的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She won't stand for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.54,1:21:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我們地獄見  丹尼  我們地獄見"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"I'll see you in hell, Danny! I'll see you in hell first!"
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.97,1:22:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但呂蓓卡死了  她已經死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But Rebecca's dead! She's dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.80,1:22:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會離開你  他會和你離婚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He'll leave you, he'll divorce you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.35,1:22:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你要怎么辦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And then what'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.15,1:22:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走就是了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll just go.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.60,1:22:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走  你要去哪兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You'll go? Go where?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.00,1:22:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在沒法再婚了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You can't remarry now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.56,1:22:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定也沒法管理一棟宅子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You certainly can't look after a house.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.40,1:22:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有家庭支持你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You don't have any family to support you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.38,1:22:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.69,1:22:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的感受  其實沒那么糟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know how you feel. It's not as bad as all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.56,1:22:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會結束\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It'll be very quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.48,1:22:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害怕  這是為了大家好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't be scared. It's all for the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.02,1:22:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人希望你在這里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No one wants you here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.18,1:22:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗里思  羅伯特  快來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Frith! Robert! Come quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.27,1:22:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一艘拖網漁船擱淺了  叫海岸警衛隊來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A trawler's run aground. Get the coast guard.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.42,1:22:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他們正趕來  老爺  -邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- They're on the way, sir. - Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.66,1:23:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在那里干什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What's he doin' down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.21,1:23:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼爾  等我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Daniel, wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.34,1:23:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  用點力  就這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Move on, now. Get up, now. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.90,1:23:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退  讓一讓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Stand back! Coming forward!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.70,1:23:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛水員下海了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Diver's down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.56,1:23:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是要撈值錢的東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Must've been something valuable.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.57,1:23:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了那艘拖網漁船\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's for the trawler.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.13,1:23:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還發現了別的東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They found somethin' else down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.58,1:23:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  好樣的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's it! Good lad!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.87,1:24:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"我歸來"號
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.86,1:24:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"我歸來"號
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.67,1:24:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都沒說  對吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I never said nothing. Did I?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.31,1:24:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在不會回來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She'll not come back now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.10,1:24:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚肯定已經把她啃食完了  對吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The fishes will have devoured her by now, ain't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.69,1:24:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.70,1:24:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該來這里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You really shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.69,1:24:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那等了  快點  都走吧  后退\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't wait there. Come on. Everybody move. Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.40,1:24:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的船里有一具尸體  跟她的發色相同\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The body was found in her boat. The same color hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.93,1:24:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有她結婚戒指上的鐫刻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And the engravings on her wedding ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.74,1:24:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問就是她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There's no doubt it's her.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.42,1:24:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't be an imbecile.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.96,1:25:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這其中肯定有個合理的解釋  對吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sure there's a perfectly logical explanation, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.06,1:25:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這很奇怪嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You don't think it's odd?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.86,1:25:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弟弟認領\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That your brother identified
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.90,1:25:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并埋葬了陌生人的尸體  當作自己的妻子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and buried the body of a stranger as his wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.04,1:25:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  賈爾斯  我不覺得奇怪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, Giles, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.33,1:25:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你那么關心  怎么不自己去問邁克西姆呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If you're so concerned, why don't you go and ask Maxim yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.33,1:25:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想  但已經好幾小時沒人看見他了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I would, but no one's seen him for hours. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.01,1:25:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  為什么警察在詢問他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What's happened? Why were the police questioning him?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.94,1:25:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他沒回過家  他們什么時候放了他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No. He's not been home. Why? When did they release him?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.44,1:25:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  你見到他后務必聯系我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}...please, do let me know when you see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.42,1:25:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  弗蘭克  謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, of course, Frank. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.68,1:25:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  好好照顧自己\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't worry. Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.89,1:26:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都結束了  她贏了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's over. She's won.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.31,1:26:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰贏了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Who's won?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.68,1:26:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蓓卡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.54,1:26:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們找到的是她的尸體\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If that's her body they found,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.60,1:26:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你之前埋葬的人是誰\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}who is it you buried?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.45,1:26:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.20,1:26:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.60,1:26:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我真相\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.95,1:26:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  我發誓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know. I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.93,1:26:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么淹死的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How did she drown?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.34,1:27:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.24,1:27:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別騙我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.16,1:27:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒有淹死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She didn't drown.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.97,1:27:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那時已經死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She was already dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.45,1:27:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的船被動了手腳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Her boat was damaged.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.87,1:27:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我干的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I damaged it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.88,1:27:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我故意的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Deliberately.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.98,1:27:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.18,1:27:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不了解她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You didn't know her.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.63,1:27:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人了解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Nobody did.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.12,1:27:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在我們度蜜月時告訴我今后的生活會如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She told me on our honeymoon how it would be.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.06,1:27:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會保留她在倫敦的公寓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How she would keep her flat in London.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.01,1:27:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一個又一個男人鬼混  連她的表哥也不放過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Her parade of men. Even her own cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.28,1:27:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please, Maxim!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.72,1:27:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很享受這樣  扮演這個角色\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She relished it. Playing the part.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.18,1:27:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的完美妻子  她知道我絕不會和她離婚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The perfect wife, knowing that I would never divorce her.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.37,1:27:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你愛她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}'Cause you loved her.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.85,1:27:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I hated her.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.99,1:27:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨她的殘酷\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hated her cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.26,1:28:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我的懦弱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I hated my cowardice.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.47,1:28:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己不會和她離婚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Knowing that I wouldn't divorce her.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.23,1:28:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己絕不能玷污家名\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Knowing I could never do that to our name.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.62,1:28:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是怎么死的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How did she die?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.54,1:28:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從倫敦回來后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When she came back from London,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.82,1:28:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說正等著費弗爾來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}she told me she was expecting a visit from Favell.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.90,1:28:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到這里時  就她一個人在\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When I got here, she was alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.63,1:28:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看起來不同尋常  臉色蒼白\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She looked different. She was pale.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.63,1:28:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去倫敦看醫生了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She'd seen a doctor in London.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.64,1:28:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說  "假設我懷了孩子  邁克斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She said, "Imagine if I had a child, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.67,1:28:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠無法證明那不是你的骨肉"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You could never prove it wasn't yours."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.52,1:28:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她奪走了我的尊嚴還不夠\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}See, it wasn't enough for her to take my pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.33,1:28:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還想奪走我的名字  我的家  我的一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She wanted to take my name, my home, everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.99,1:28:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她說  "來啊  邁克斯  動手吧"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And she said, "Go on, Max, do it."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.31,1:28:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"你只需要扣下扳機  之后你就自由了"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"All you have to do is pull the trigger and you'll be free."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.65,1:28:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.39,1:29:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子彈徑直穿過了她的身體\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Bullet went straight through her.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.89,1:29:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她沒有馬上倒下  只是站在原地\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She didn't fall right away. She just stood there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.92,1:29:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無比平靜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.76,1:29:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像釋懷了一般\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Almost relieved.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.35,1:29:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她就死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And then she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.06,1:29:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來我以為你還愛著呂蓓卡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All this time I thought you still loved Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.92,1:30:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么不告訴我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.02,1:30:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不出口\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.29,1:30:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太害怕會失去你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was so afraid I'd have lost you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.82,1:30:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去報警吧  告訴他們一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Go to the police, tell them everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.74,1:30:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不知道  你不會受牽連\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You didn't know. Nothing'll happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.03,1:30:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想再和我扯上關系  我也能理解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I understand if you want nothing more to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.22,1:30:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的選擇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.20,1:30:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弄錯了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You made a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.68,1:30:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認錯了尸體\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}identifying the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.12,1:30:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是因為你太悲痛受創\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was the grief, the trauma.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.69,1:30:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們沒人知道真相  其他人永遠不會知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Nobody knows but us. Nobody will ever know.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.77,1:30:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒有贏  邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, she hasn't won, Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.11,1:31:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒有贏\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She hasn't won.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.08,1:31:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會讓她贏\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We won't let her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.03,1:31:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用和他們說什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You don't have to speak to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.51,1:31:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體起立  尊敬的詹姆斯·克勞奇先生來了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All stand for the Right Honorable James Crouch.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.27,1:31:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.79,1:31:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肅靜  大家安靜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Order! Settle down.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.78,1:31:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...  坐下  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is the... Sit down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.96,1:31:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次審理是為調查\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is the coroner's inquest
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.88,1:31:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蓓卡·德溫特的死因\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}into the discovery of the body of Rebecca de Winter.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.61,1:31:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此案目前不是刑事訴訟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is not currently a criminal proceeding.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.17,1:31:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是來查明德溫特夫人是怎么死的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We are here only to ascertain how Mrs. de Winter died.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.09,1:31:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本庭現在聽取\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The court will now hear
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.34,1:31:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯警局韋爾奇警長的證詞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}from Detective Welch of the Kerrith police.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.48,1:31:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韋爾奇警長\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Detective Welch.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.65,1:32:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特先生去年指認的那具尸體...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The body Mr. de Winter identified last year...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.14,1:32:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是他妻子的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}was not his wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.07,1:32:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  呂蓓卡·德溫特的尸體\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}In fact, Rebecca de Winter's body
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.60,1:32:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從她的船艙里打撈到的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}was recovered from the cabin of her boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.87,1:32:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我很困惑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That troubled me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.38,1:32:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣令人困惑的還有船的破損情況\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}As did the nature of the damage to the vessel.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.55,1:32:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And what was that nature?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.60,1:32:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發現吃水線下方有四個洞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We found four holes below the waterline
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.77,1:32:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形狀和用魚叉鑿出的洞一致\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}consistent with those made by a ship's gaff.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.49,1:32:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-或用長釘  -說明什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Or spike. - Suggesting what?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.64,1:32:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明船是被蓄意鑿洞弄沉的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That the boat was deliberately scuttled.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.94,1:32:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死因裁判官大人  在我看來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}In my opinion, Mr. Coroner,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.12,1:32:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次審理只能作出兩種裁決  非此即彼\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}this inquest can return one of only two verdicts.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.35,1:32:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此案不是自殺就是他殺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Suicide or unlawful killing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.99,1:32:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夫人去世那天去過倫敦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Your wife made a trip to London the day she died.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.30,1:32:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.40,1:32:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在警方錄的口供中說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}In your statement to the police, you say your wife seemed
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.98,1:32:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夫人回來后似乎"心事重重  郁郁寡歡"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Preoccupied and unhappy" when she returned.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.72,1:32:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別表現得太防備  回答問題時保持鎮靜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't be defensive. Answer their questions calmly.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.63,1:33:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去倫敦做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What was the purpose of her trip?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.22,1:33:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.26,1:33:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正常嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Was it normal for your wife
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.97,1:33:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子不和自己丈夫商量這種事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}not to discuss such matters with her husband?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.68,1:33:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在暗示我的婚姻有問題嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are you implying there were problems in my marriage?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.34,1:33:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想弄清楚為什么去年\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm trying to understand how you apparently failed
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.13,1:33:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并沒認出尸體不是你妻子的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to recognize your own wife last year.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.47,1:33:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那時已在海上漂了兩個月\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She'd been two months at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.01,1:33:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她漂流了20英里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She drifted 20 miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.30,1:33:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸體已經泡腫腐爛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She was bloated, decomposing,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.68,1:33:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的胳膊沒了  面容盡毀\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}her arms ripped off, ` and there was nothing left of her face.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.76,1:33:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肅靜  肅靜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Order! Order!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.47,1:33:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛真是愚蠢又傲慢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was arrogant and stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.88,1:33:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我慌了  -不  你只是很激動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- I lost my nerve. - No, you were passionate.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.22,1:33:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會相信你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They'll believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.34,1:33:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰知道她去倫敦見了醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Who else knows she saw a doctor in London?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.26,1:33:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  我  還有那位醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You, me, and the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.59,1:33:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不可能找到任何物證的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They're not likely to find any physical evidence.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.01,1:33:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟尸體在海上漂了那么久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not after so long at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.34,1:33:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位醫生是他們僅有的證據\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The doctor is all they have.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.26,1:34:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和費弗爾先生說了這不歡迎他  但他非要來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I did tell Mr. Favell he wasn't welcome, but he insisted.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.26,1:34:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  丹弗斯太太\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you, Mrs. Danvers.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.13,1:34:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想要什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What the hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.38,1:34:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一杯威士忌蘇打就挺好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Another whiskey and soda would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.97,1:34:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事關呂蓓卡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's about Rebecca,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.22,1:34:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要不要先叫你妻子去睡覺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}so you might want to send your wife off to bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.34,1:34:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪兒都不去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.76,1:34:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和呂蓓卡間的事我全都知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know all about you and Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.13,1:34:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.93,1:34:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你全都知道  是嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know all about that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.22,1:34:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差點被我抓到  費弗爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You were close, Favell.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.38,1:34:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那天晚上我抓到了你倆在一起...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If I'd caught you here that night with her...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.05,1:34:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上他根本沒來過\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was never here that night.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.35,1:34:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她確實邀請了我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But she did invite me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.43,1:34:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是關鍵\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And that's the point.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.51,1:34:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自殺就是謀殺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Suicide or foul play,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.13,1:34:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是這么說的  對嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that's what the chap said, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.38,1:34:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約別人見面...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Now, inviting someone over...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.39,1:34:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來不像是一個準備自殺的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}doesn't really sound like the sort of thing one would do
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.59,1:34:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會做的事  對嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}if one was planning to end it all, does it?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.01,1:35:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去這一年  這事一直折磨著我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And that's what's been driving me mad this last year.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.80,1:35:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真相開始浮出水面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But it's beginning to make sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.38,1:35:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她終于決定要離開你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She finally decided to leave you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.26,1:35:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就把她殺了  對嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is that why you killed her?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.93,1:35:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有證據\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You've no proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.76,1:35:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你和我各執一詞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's your word against mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.76,1:35:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.13,1:35:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你和呂蓓卡各執一詞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's your word against Rebecca's.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.80,1:35:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"收到此信后來曼陀麗莊園\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Come to Manders when you get this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.22,1:35:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事相告\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've something to tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.93,1:35:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盼盡快與你相見  呂蓓卡上"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I want to see you as soon as possible. Rebecca."
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.22,1:35:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.43,1:35:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-滾出我的房子  -別被他激怒  邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Get out of my house. - Don't rise to it, Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.72,1:35:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  別被我激怒了  邁克斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes. Don't rise to it, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.59,1:35:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我只是來感謝你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I only came by to thank you, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.38,1:35:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些年來  你一直都很慷慨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You've been so generous over the years,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.42,1:35:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們這么多男人分享你的妻子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}sharing your wife with so many of us chaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.55,1:35:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  我還想要不要試試勾搭你的新夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Actually, I wondered if I might try my luck with the new one.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.55,1:36:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了  這就是我跟你說的暴脾氣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There it is. There's that temper I told you about.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.55,1:36:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要多少錢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How much do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.47,1:36:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她比看起來要聰明  對嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She's cleverer than she looks, this one, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.09,1:36:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像流血了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Seems to be a spot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.63,1:36:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Dearie me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.14,1:36:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她說得對\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She's right, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.84,1:36:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是有錢人  邁克斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm not a rich man, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.38,1:36:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太沉迷賭博  不可能有錢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, I'm too fond of gambling for that,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.97,1:36:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我確實喜歡上了某種生活方式\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but I do have a certain lifestyle that I've come to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.97,1:36:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概一萬英鎊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I imagine I could get by on around...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.76,1:36:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能換我這張便條\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}£10,000 for the note
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.80,1:36:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且換我明天出庭作證時不提此事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and my silence when I take the stand tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.63,1:36:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是敲詐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.47,1:36:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你要干什么  -報警\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- What are you doing? - Calling the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.80,1:36:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  報警啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah. Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.59,1:36:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許還能被關在同一間牢房\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Might even put us in the same cell.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.76,1:36:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過關不了多久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not for long, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.51,1:37:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該會被絞刑處死  邁克西姆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I imagine you're looking at the noose, Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.59,1:37:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應韋爾奇警長的要求\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}At Inspector Welch's request,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.59,1:37:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早的庭審有所變動\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}there's a change to this morning's proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.72,1:37:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在聽取\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We shall now hear
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.09,1:37:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼陀麗莊園的管家丹弗斯太太的證詞\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}from the de Winters' housekeeper, Mrs. Danvers.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.05,1:37:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說  曼陀麗內沒什么事是你不知道的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Safe to say not much occurs at Manderley
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.18,1:37:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或未經你準許的  我說得對嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}without your knowledge or say-so, would I be right?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.01,1:37:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責確保莊園的有序運轉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I ensure the smooth running of the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.47,1:37:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你才會發現\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Which is how you came to be aware
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.97,1:37:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已故德溫特夫人和費弗爾先生之間的關系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}of the late Mrs. de Winter's relationship with Mr. Favell.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.18,1:37:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他們很親密\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, I was aware they were, intimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.84,1:37:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我家夫人的私生活是她的私事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But my lady's private affairs were her own.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.80,1:37:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理應如此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So they should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.97,1:37:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為案情十分反常\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But since these circumstances are far from normal,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.63,1:37:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你能當庭分享下你昨晚和我說的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}perhaps you'd share with the court what you told me last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.76,1:37:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得知有一張給費弗爾先生的便條\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I learned of a note addressed to Mr. Favell.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.26,1:38:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我力勸他給你看那張便條\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I urged him to share that note with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.47,1:38:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特先生似乎很不想讓法庭發現那張便條\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A note Mr. de Winter seemed keen to keep from this court.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.22,1:38:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.97,1:38:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便條的內容是邀請費弗爾先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The note was inviting Mr. Favell
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.05,1:38:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在德溫特夫人去世的那天晚上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to join Mrs. de Winter at the house...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.09,1:38:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去莊園見她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}the night my lady died.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.59,1:38:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特先生想用錢交換那張便條\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mr. de Winter offered money in exchange for that note.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.73,1:38:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便條是呂蓓卡·德溫特寫的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The note was from Rebecca de Winter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.63,1:38:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.26,1:38:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她寫了有急事要告訴他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She wrote she had urgent news to share with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.43,1:38:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,費弗爾先生收到的開價是多少錢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And how much was Mr. Favell offered?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.01,1:38:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一萬鎊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}£10,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.43,1:38:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張支票\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A check...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.89,1:38:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是德溫特先生開的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}written by Mr. de Winter...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.55,1:38:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來換取那張便條\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}in exchange for the note.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.93,1:38:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你憑什么這么說  僅憑一張支票\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where does it say that? All you have is a check.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.47,1:38:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-說明不了用途  -肅靜  女士  肅靜\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Nothing to say what it's for. - Order! Madam, order.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.05,1:38:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯太太  你認為\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Danvers, do you think it's likely
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.22,1:38:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蓓卡·德溫特有否可能是溺水自殺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Rebecca de Winter drowned herself?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.43,1:39:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  先生  我不這么認為\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, sir. I do not.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.38,1:39:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她去世前的幾周里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}In the weeks, leading up to her death,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.26,1:39:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她變得倦怠乏力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}she had become fatigued
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.18,1:39:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是感覺惡心想吐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and was feeling sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.84,1:39:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她讓我放寬了她的褲子腰帶\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And she asked me to let out the waistband in her trousers.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.80,1:39:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的肚子變大了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Her belly was growing.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.26,1:39:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特夫人去世那天去了趟倫敦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. de Winter went to London the day she died.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.30,1:39:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有沒有說原因\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Did she say why?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.51,1:39:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒有  -奇怪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- No. - Odd.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.63,1:39:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是非常私人的事情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It must've been something deeply personal
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.34,1:39:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不想讓我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}for her to have kept that from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.93,1:39:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說  見她的醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Like, say, an appointment with her doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.51,1:39:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是你們料想的家庭醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not her family doctor, as you might expect,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.51,1:39:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是某個低調謹慎的醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but someone discreet.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.09,1:39:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她躲避窺探\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Away from prying eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.43,1:39:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎并不想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}as if news of her condition
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.76,1:39:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓別人知道她的身體狀況\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}was something she wished to keep private.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.38,1:39:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只愿意告訴她的情人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A wish to share only with her lover,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.38,1:39:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克·費弗爾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Jack Favell.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.38,1:39:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這該死的殺人犯  你是該死的殺人犯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You murdering bastard. You're a murdering bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.88,1:39:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還殺了我的孩子  我希望他們把你絞死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}With my child! I hope they hang you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.26,1:39:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他們把你絞死  你殺了呂蓓卡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I hope they hang you! You murdered Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.47,1:39:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結論只可能有兩種\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Only two possible verdicts.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.14,1:40:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你贊同  先生  本案完全沒有自殺動機\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I hope you agree, sir, that there's no motive at all for suicide.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.34,1:40:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但顯然有謀殺動機\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But a clear one for murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.67,1:40:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審理暫緩  等待刑事調查結果\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This inquest is suspended pending a criminal investigation.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.01,1:40:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們  我宣布休庭\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ladies and gentlemen, court is adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.55,1:40:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人能凌駕于法律之上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Nobody's above the law.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.14,1:40:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我  放開\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Get your hands off me! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.80,1:40:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯太太\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Danvers.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.51,1:40:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也沒別說  他們沒有任何證據\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Say nothing. They can't prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.26,1:40:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要她的日程簿  日記  通訊錄\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I want her appointment books, diaries, address books,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.34,1:40:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭賬本  所有東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}household finances, everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.26,1:40:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在某個時間見過那醫生  并付了他錢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She saw that doctor sometime and she paid him.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.34,1:40:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅  開始打電話詢問倫敦的婦科醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Roe, start placing calls to women specialists in London.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.93,1:41:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.93,1:41:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  請問你們有搜查許可嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sorry, do you have permission to search this place?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.29,1:41:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呂
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.01,1:41:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德溫特夫人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. de Winter?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.59,1:41:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-弗蘭克  -怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Frank! - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.68,1:41:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要她的支票  銀行對賬單\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I need her checks, her bank statements.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.76,1:41:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何寫有她醫生的姓名和地址的東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Anything that has the name and address of her doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.22,1:41:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  是這些\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Right. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.47,1:41:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你需要什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know what you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.51,1:41:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我需要找到醫生  -你要找她的醫生  這里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- I need a doctor. - You need her doctor? There.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.83,1:41:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}約·貝克醫生合伙診所
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.30,1:41:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就是這個\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.59,1:41:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真無恥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Shame on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.59,1:41:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太無恥了  你竟然站在他那邊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Shame on you for taking his side.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.72,1:42:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒站在任何人那邊  丹弗斯太太  我...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm not taking anyone's side, Mrs. Danvers. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.09,1:42:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你  弗蘭克\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And you, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.30,1:42:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天舔著德溫特夫人的靴子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Licking Mr. de Winter's boots by day,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.05,1:42:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上抓撓小屋的門\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and pawing at the cottage door at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.09,1:42:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個小男孩一樣啜泣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Sobbing like a schoolboy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.34,1:42:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看不起你們所有人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She despised you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.34,1:42:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫敦的那些男人  參加曼陀麗舞會的那些男人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The men in London, the men at the Manderley parties.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.72,1:42:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都只是她的玩物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You were nothing but playthings for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.64,1:42:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人為什么不能找樂子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And why shouldn't a woman amuse herself?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.47,1:42:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她隨心所欲地生活  我的呂蓓卡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She lived her life as she pleased, my Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.38,1:42:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪男人不得不殺了她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No wonder a man had to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.01,1:42:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很心痛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It must have hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.93,1:42:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你在世上唯一的朋友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Knowing your only friend in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.38,1:42:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那樣的秘密帶進墳墓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}took a secret like that to her grave.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.05,1:42:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾好你的東西  丹弗斯太太\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pack your bags, Mrs. Danvers.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.97,1:42:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你天黑之前就走人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I expect you gone by nightfall.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.25,1:44:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}倫敦哈利街79b\N約·貝克醫生合伙診所
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.18,1:44:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-小姐  有什么事  -真抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Miss? - Terribly sorry,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.68,1:44:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘拿手提包了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've left my purse.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.38,1:44:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見的是哪位醫生  小姐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Who was it you saw, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.47,1:44:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰·貝克醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Dr. John Baker.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.34,1:44:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.97,1:45:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那兒等著\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wait there.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.76,1:45:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-貝克醫生診所  -晚上好  塔斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Dr. Baker, sir. - Good evening, Tas.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.80,1:45:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"丹弗斯"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Danvers."
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.93,1:45:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過無數病人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I see so many patients.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.22,1:45:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can't remember her.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.84,1:45:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到她的病歷也許就能想起來\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maybe it'll come back when you see her file.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.13,1:45:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看看病例\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It would have been more convenient
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.68,1:45:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然會更方便\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to read the file to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.09,1:45:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會盡力幫忙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We'll do what we can to help.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.52,1:46:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不該這樣\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, no. This is not as it should be.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.27,1:46:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去哪兒了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where's she gone now?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.15,1:46:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.04,1:46:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}請勿讓患者接觸
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.98,1:46:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在這里的年輕女子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The young woman who was here.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.94,1:46:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.76,1:46:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問問我的秘書\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll have a word with my secretary.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.50,1:46:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}X光結果顯示子宮內有根深蒂固的腫塊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.02,1:46:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能把病歷放錯地方了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's possible she misplaced it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.65,1:46:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩有沒有可能離開這里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This girl. Is there any way she could get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.75,1:46:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}認為是惡性子宮肉瘤
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.60,1:46:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看了  僅此而已\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I read it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.86,1:47:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒改過貝克醫生半個字\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I haven't changed a word Dr. Baker wrote.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.67,1:47:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蓓卡·丹弗斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Rebecca Danvers.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.86,1:47:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  現在我想起來了  很可怕的病\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, now I remember. Terrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.56,1:47:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是她的真名\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That wasn't her real name.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.27,1:47:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也沒懷孕\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And she wasn't pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.61,1:47:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她為什么要用假名\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then why would she use a false name?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.44,1:47:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為什么要大老遠跑來倫敦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why would she come all the way to London
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.77,1:47:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預約你給她看診\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to make an appointment with you
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.07,1:47:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不找她的家庭醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and not her family doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.73,1:47:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許她不想讓家人知道這個噩耗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Perhaps she wanted to spare her family the news.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.19,1:47:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  知道孩子不是她丈夫的嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That the baby wasn't her husband's?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.52,1:47:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警長  我不是那種婦科醫生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Inspector, I am not that kind of women's specialist.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.56,1:47:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是產科醫師\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm not an obstetrician.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.27,1:47:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的專長是腫瘤學\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}My field is oncology.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.90,1:47:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我治療生殖系統的癌癥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I treat cancers of the reproductive system.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.19,1:47:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她腫脹  疲乏\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The bloating, the fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.44,1:47:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是常見癥狀\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They're common symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.19,1:47:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她患了癌癥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She had cancer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.90,1:47:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想告訴杰克·費弗爾的就是這事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There's her news for Jack Favell.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.69,1:47:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這并不能證明她是自殺的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That doesn't prove she killed herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.06,1:47:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會想遭受病痛折磨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She wouldn't have wanted to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.31,1:47:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  她也這么跟我說的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, she told me as much.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.19,1:47:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她出現癥狀時已經是晚期\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She was very advanced by the time she was symptomatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.15,1:47:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次見她是在四月\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Saw her first in April,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.31,1:47:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到五月時  她顯然已經病重得無法醫治\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}by May, it was clear she was too far gone for treatment.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.86,1:47:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只剩下幾周時間\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She only had weeks
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.94,1:48:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且會遭受巨大痛苦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and the pain would have been considerable.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.19,1:48:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如何自盡的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How did she do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.65,1:48:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把船取出來鑿穿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She took out her boat and scuttled it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.44,1:48:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把自己淹死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She drowned herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:53.55,1:48:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真走運  邁克斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Stroke of luck for you there, Max.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.97,1:49:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定認為你贏了  對吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I bet you think you've won, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.56,1:49:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許法律不能懲罰你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, maybe the law can't get you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.61,1:49:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我仍然可以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I still can.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.02,1:49:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有別的話想說嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is there anything else you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.40,1:49:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有就趕緊說\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If there is, you better say it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.81,1:49:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我最恨她哪一點嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you know what I hate her for most?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.52,1:49:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她奪走了你的純真\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's what she's taken from you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.44,1:49:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一去不復返了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's gone forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.30,1:49:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所鐘愛的那些幽默  朝氣  迷惘的神情\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That funny, young, lost look I loved so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.63,1:49:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不再是從前那個女孩了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're not that person anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.92,1:49:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為這個恨她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't hate her for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.12,1:50:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}呂
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.02,1:50:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么東西著火了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What's that burning?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.73,1:50:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  是曼陀麗莊園\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, my God, that's Manderley.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.73,1:50:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  離開那里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on! Get away from there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.73,1:50:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開草坪  快走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Get off the lawn! Go! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.15,1:50:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開草坪  弗里思  快離開草坪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Get off the lawn! Frith, get off the lawn!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.44,1:50:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋里有多少人  大家都逃出來了嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How many people are inside? Is everyone out?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.98,1:50:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  老爺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.05,1:50:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  發生了什么  克拉麗斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You all right? What happened, Clarice?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.97,1:50:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見她了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.77,1:51:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思  你看見誰了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What do you mean? Who did you see?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.19,1:51:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯太太\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Danvers.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.94,1:51:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Help her! Help her!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.27,1:51:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水管在哪兒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where are the hoses?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.52,1:51:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪里  她在哪里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where is she? Where is she!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.81,1:51:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去船庫了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She went to the boat house.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.94,1:52:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯太太  求求你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Danvers! Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.40,1:52:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別站在懸崖邊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please come away.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.15,1:52:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我幫助你  我這就是在幫你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You asked for my help. Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.11,1:52:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯太太  求你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mrs. Danvers, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.73,1:52:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他殺了我唯一愛過的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He killed the only person I loved.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.44,1:52:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓你們奪走曼陀麗莊園\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can't let you have Manderley.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.65,1:52:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是屬于我們的  你明白嗎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was ours, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:40.81,1:52:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必這么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.36,1:52:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你會支持他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know you'll stand by him.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.19,1:52:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你永遠不會知曉幸福的滋味\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But you'll never know happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.32,1:52:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.23,1:53:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚  我又夢到我去了曼陀麗莊園\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Last night, I dreamt I went to Manderley again.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.52,1:54:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夢見了丹弗斯太太和呂蓓卡\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I dreamt of Mrs. Danvers and of Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.90,1:54:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今早我醒來后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But this morning I woke up
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.76,1:54:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把逝者拋諸腦后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and left the dead behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.86,1:54:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坐在鏡子前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And as I sit before the mirror
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.56,1:54:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身處我們在開羅的悶熱房間里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}in our stuffy little room in Cairo,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.52,1:54:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是其中一站  直到我們找到真正的家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}just another stop on our quest to find a real home,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.31,1:54:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看清我現在變成了什么樣子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can see the woman I am now.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.57,1:54:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我做出了正確決定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And I know that I have made the right decision...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.26,1:54:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救了唯一值得為之赴湯蹈火的東西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to save the one thing worth walking through flames for.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.76,1:54:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Love.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.76,1:55:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(192,80)\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\fs40\fad(1900,1500)\1a&H70&\bord0\shad0\fsp3\frx5}蝴蝶夢
